{"type":null,"faqId":49982,"title":"华为智能手表_手表有哪些特色功能？","answer":"<body style=\"clear:both; padding-left:10px; padding-top:5px; padding-right:5px; padding-bottom:5px\"><div id=\"body53678462\"><p id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022329133__p64451931102438\">HUAWEI WATCH （以下简称智能手表、手表）是一款集运动健康、语音服务、信息助手为一体的智能手表。它主要为商务人群、科技型男、注重运动健康、追求生活品质的人群设计。</p><p id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022329133__p53223935102438\">智能手表采用传统圆形表盘，外观复刻经典兼具时尚与科技。选用蓝宝石玻璃（为人工合成蓝宝石），搭配通过严格皮肤过敏测试的表带，带给您安全舒适的佩戴感受。同时配备多款精美可选的皮质表带和不锈钢表带，方便您在不同场景进行搭配。</p><p id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022329133__p57600205102555\">智能手表支持以下功能：</p><ul id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022329133__ul4220391810263\"><li id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022329133__li749625410263\">更换表盘（多款精心设计的经典、数字、运动表盘。）</li><li id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022329133__li14398365192735\">蓝牙通话 （手表升级到M2D28及以上版本后支持通话功能）</li><li id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022329133__li337180510267\">信息提醒（来电、短信、邮件、app消息推送等）</li><li id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022329133__li41880308102611\">语音服务（你好，安卓）</li><li id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022329133__li32830079102615\">运动状态识别（走、跑、登高、走楼梯）</li><li id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022329133__li29160949102619\">运动数据统计（单次、全天）</li><li id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022329133__li51519734102622\">卡路里统计</li><li id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022329133__li47563129102626\">站立数据统计</li><li id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022329133__li14202358102630\">心率检测</li><li id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022329133__li16720668102635\">蓝牙</li><li id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022329133__li30981435102638\">地图导航</li><li id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022329133__li25203331102642\">时间显示</li><li id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022329133__li2319233102646\">世界时钟</li><li id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022329133__li1228789102650\">秒表</li><li id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022329133__li46217902102715\">计时器</li><li id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022329133__li58217420102719\">闹钟</li><li id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022329133__li41287252102723\">支持应用市场中适配手表的多种app</li></ul><p id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022329133__p3361004395440\">感谢您支持并使用华为手表，关于手表支付、消息回复等更多操作，请您在Wi-Fi环境下参阅视频教程：<a href=\"http://v.youku.com/v_show/id_XMTQyODE3NjY2MA==.html\" target=\"_blank\">http://v.youku.com/v_show/id_XMTQyODE3NjY2MA==.html</a></p><p id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022329133__p35750757174320\">如有需要，您可以联系热线（4008308300）通过短信获取该内容。</p></div></body>","faqTypeId":497,"faqType":"产品介绍","useful":8,"unUseful":6,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"zh-cn_topic_0022329133","faqTypeCode":"Wearable_Device-Product-Introduction","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1448627735000,"seriesProductName":"Mercury-G00,Mercury-G01,Mercury-G10,Mercury-G101,Mercury-G201","visitedTimes":376,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"特色，特点，卖点，主要功能","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}